      <minor />
      <comment>general fixes using [[Project:AWB|AWB]]</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox NRHP
  | name =Cobble Hill Historic District
  | nrhp_type = hd
  | image = Atlantic Ave Tunnel.jpg
  | caption = Atlantic Avenue Tunnel, 2009
  | location= [[Brooklyn, New York]]
