| Years_active        = 1945–1984
| Label               = [[Decca Records|Decca]], [[Polydor Records|Polydor]], Spot Records, [[Columbia Records|CBS Records]], [[Transatlantic Records]], [[Fontana Records|Fontana]], [[RAK Records]], [[Tempo Records|Tempo]], [[Brain Records]], [[Liberty Records|Liberty]], Atlantic/Metronome, [[77 Records]]
