* ''[[Star (magazine)|Star]]''
* ''[[The Globe (tabloid)|The Globe]]''
* ''[[National Examiner]]''
* ''[[Sun (supermarket tabloid)|Sun]]''
* ''[[Country Weekly]]''
* ''[[Muscle &amp; Fitness]]''
* ''[[Muscle &amp; Fitness Hers]]''
* ''[[Shape (magazine)|Shape]]''
* ''[[Men's Fitness]]''
* ''[[Flex Magazine|Flex]]''
* ''[[Natural Health (magazine)|Natural Health]]''
* ''[[Radar (magazine)|Radar Online]]''

