''For other uses, see [[Titus (disambiguation)]]''

{{Infobox saint
|name=Saint Titus
|birth_date=1st century [[AD]]
|death_date=96 or 107 [[AD]]
|feast_day=January 26&lt;br /&gt;February 6 (General Roman Calendar 1845-1969)
|venerated_in=[[Roman Catholic Church]]&lt;br /&gt;[[Eastern Orthodox Churches]]&lt;br /&gt;[[Eastern Catholic Churches]]&lt;br /&gt;[[Lutheranism]]&lt;br /&gt; [[Anglican Communion]]
