| AmF&lt;sub&gt;3&lt;/sub&gt;|| Pink or light [[beige]]|| [[Hexagonal crystal system||hexagonal]], LaF&lt;sub&gt;3&lt;/sub&gt;|| 7.04 &lt;ref name=&quot;katz&quot;&gt;{{cite book|author = F. Weigel, J. Katz, G. Seaborg ''et al.''|title = The Chemistry of the Actinide Elements|place=Moscow|publisher = Mir| year = 1997|volume = 2|isbn = 5-03-001885-9}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;{{cite journal|last1=Nave|first1=S.|last2=Haire|first2=R.|last3=Huray|first3=Paul|title=Magnetic properties of actinide elements having the 5f^{6} and 5f^{7} electronic configurations|journal=Physical Review B|volume=28|pages=2317|year=1983|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.28.2317}}&lt;/ref&gt;||-|| 7.255|| 9.53
